Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 1st May 2024
Thank you for choosing to play our game! We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and secure your data when you use our games.
1. Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information
Account Info:
If you sign in using Google or Apple, we collect your email address and profile picture.
1.2 Non-Personal Information
Game Data:
We collect data like your device type, operating system, language settings, and game activity.
Unique Identifiers:
We gather unique device identifiers to help improve your gaming experience.
2. How We Use Your Information
Game Functionality:
To enable you to save your game progress and settings.
Improvements:
To analyze and enhance game features and user experience.
Ads:
To show you personalized ads based on the information collected.
3. Legal Compliance
We adhere to privacy laws applicable to our games and do not collect information from users under the age of 13 without parental consent.
4. Advertising
Third-Party Ads:
Our games include ads from networks like Unity Ads, Google AdMob, and IronSource. These networks may use your data to personalize ads. For more details, please see their privacy policies.
Unity Ads
Google AdMob
IronSource
5. Analytics
We use tools like Unity Analytics to understand how our games are used. These tools collect data anonymously, focusing on improving the games.
6. Data Protection
We take precautions to protect your data, using security measures like encryption and secure servers.
7. User Rights
Access and Control:
You can request access to or deletion of your personal information at any time.
Opt-Out:
You can opt out of personalized ads and data analytics within the game settings.
8. International Data Transfers
Your data may be transferred internationally to ensure game functionality and adherence to legal standards.
9. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes via in-game notifications or our website.
10. Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us at
contact@w3villa.com